            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2056.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> finely</p><p>Once the leek has softened, increase the heat to medium-high and add the <strong>courgette</strong> to the pan and cook for 4-5 min further or until cooked</p>",
